      "content": "but like, if we look at the data, isn't it basically a fact that more guns equals more crime? the constitutional stuff feels more like an opinion or a legal technicality, whereas the stats on violence are more concrete. wouldn't you say the scientific evidence usually carries more weight in this debate?",
